<p><b>What are the 7 standards for housekeeping?</b> 7S of Good Housekeeping- stands for Sort, Set in Order, Shine, Standardize, Sustain or Self Discipline, Safety and Spirit. Sort Clarify necessary/unnecessary things, and dispose of unnecessary things. Remove potentially unsafe /broken items from the area in order to utilize working space efficiently.</p>
